original_text: Then Jephthah came to his home at Mizpah. And behold, his daughter came out to meet him with tambourines and with dances. She was his only child; besides her he had neither son nor daughter.
korean_text: 입다가 미스바에 있는 자기 집에 이를 때에 보라 그의 딸이 소고를 잡고 춤추며 나와서 영접하니 이는 그의 무남독녀라

sentences.original_text: Then Jephthah came to his home at Mizpah.
sentences.korean_translation: 그때 입다가 자기 집 미스바로 돌아왔습니다.
